According to [ChatGPT](https://chatgpt.com/)

> it's best practice to also add rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" so the new tab cannot access your page (prevents a small security risk).

So in our `href` elements we also should add \"rel=\"noopenernoreferrer\" for security

``` html
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/theneedledrop" target="_blank">
```
